{"tid":472622,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"轉台一問","createTime":"2017-11-18T12:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T11:32:59.000Z","uid":110533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"462cb2fcbe4749507f4d3538144cf7bc366a053f","tid":472622,"uid":110533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:05:02.000Z","msg":"本身用緊CSL... 同人SHARE用..<br />\n9號係帳單日<br />\n10號 會計另一筆錢<br />\n10-18號係預繳日<br />\n<br />\n本人同其他share既人 9號前 各自轉左HKBN...<br />\n本身應該今日轉到...<br />\n但係岩岩先收到HKBN通知 話得我轉唔到<br />\n (佢話我個電話號碼唔係本身CSL個登記號碼)<br />\n<br />\n咁我CSL係咪要俾多個月錢?(成600蚊)...<br />\n<br />\nHKBN到今日先通知我轉唔到 我月頭就申請(連張SIM卡都啟動埋)..以為乜都搞晒<br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以免到果600蚊?"},{"pid":"c26487ba235e34102bcb00c6b7db5c1d4be31195","tid":472622,"uid":150379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ed59eed700233c998e082b403775dd13c0dc331","tid":472622,"uid":145233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62efc40a646359ee536344617a7e24bb96aaec4e","tid":472622,"uid":154653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecfb61a5a593675fd84027a51261a6d1d1dff0c4","tid":472622,"uid":148111,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ed995509824d79f319d314d2764620382cc4a50","tid":472622,"uid":148506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f2efe4d07dbcb8a43e41f13c94963bd6a4fd9d5","tid":472622,"uid":140310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dfeb63126428d5cfa04b375893a8b2ef67363df","tid":472622,"uid":149174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"556d39a6463056f099f2e41f1648e1135166e132","tid":472622,"uid":148123,"like":0,"dislike